---
description: Security and compliance guardrails
globs: ["**/*auth*", "**/*user*", "**/*patient*", "**/*privacy*", "**/*consent*"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- Minimize collection, storage, and exposure of personal data.
- Do not log sensitive fields.
- Prefer deny-by-default access patterns.
- Flag any change impacting retention, auditability, consent, or data sharing.
